name: Lost Woods (deblasei)
description:
Welcome to Lost Woods, A re-skin of the shooter Tutorial.

Modifications include - 

  • Background change, including 3 different times for the game (Day, Evening, night)
  • Enemy and Player Sprite designs
  • Obstacle Re Designs
  • Decoration designs (Flowers and stumps)
  • A new font
  • 2 brand new levels!

Game created by Isabella DeBlase with the use of CAS 117 coding, sprites, and directions
